    "comment": "I am changing my vote from NO to YES on supporting the IO & VacuumLabs: Enhancing Plutus - Performance, Correctness, and Usability proposal.\n\n
    While funding is extremely competitive this year, now is not the appropriate time to cut spending on features/enhancements that will better position Cardano making the protocol more attractive and competitive. \n\I believe Cardano has mostly lost the DeFi race and also that we should be prioritizing features strictly based on validated market/cusotmer demand in order to achieve adoption. That being said, I beleive it prudent to invest selectively into the effort of winning DeFi market share.  \n"
